INSERT INTO `incident` VALUES (1016,'INC001006','Unable to print from accounting department – paper jam persistent.','unable print accounting department paper jam persistent','Users in accounting are reporting a persistent paper jam on the shared printer. They’ve attempted to clear the jam manually and restarted the printer. Error message is \'Paper Jam – Clear Obstruction\'. The impact on payroll processing is significant.','New','USER00012','ServiceDeskAgent1','2024-10-27 14:15:00.000000','Phone','High','High',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(1017,'INC001007','VPN connection drops intermittently – Windows 10 laptop.','vpn connection drops intermittently windows 10 laptop','User reports frequent VPN disconnections, primarily on their Windows 10 laptop. Connectivity appears stable otherwise. They\'ve tried rebooting their laptop and router.  The issue is preventing remote access to critical financial data. The VPN logs show a brief disconnect every 15-20 minutes.','Work In Progress','USER00035','ServiceDeskAgent2','2024-10-27 14:45:00.000000','Email','Medium','Medium',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(1018,'INC001008','Salesforce login failing – SSO authentication error.','salesforce login failing sso authentication error','Multiple users in sales are unable to log in to Salesforce, receiving an SSO authentication error. The error message is \'Authentication Failed – Contact Your Administrator\'.  The SSO logs indicate a temporary issue with the identity provider’s response. This is impacting ability to access customer records.','Resolved','USER00008','ServiceDeskAgent1','2024-10-27 15:00:00.000000','Chat','High','High','SystemEngineer1','2024-10-27 16:30:00.000000',NULL,NULL),(1019,'INC001009','Slow email sync – Outlook web app unresponsive.','slow email sync outlook web app unresponsive','Users are reporting very slow email synchronization in the Outlook web app. Sending and receiving emails are significantly delayed. They\'ve cleared their browser cache, but the problem persists. The issue impacts productivity across several departments.','New','USER00051','ServiceDeskAgent3','2024-10-27 15:30:00.000000','Walk-up','Medium','Medium',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(1020,'INC001010','Cannot access shared drive – permission denied error.','access shared drive permission denied error','User is receiving a \'Permission Denied\' error when attempting to access the shared finance drive. They were recently moved to a different team.  The group membership may need updating. This prevents access to critical financial documents.','Work In Progress','USER00022','ServiceDeskAgent2','2024-10-27 16:00:00.000000','Email','Medium','Medium',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(1021,'INC001011','Microsoft Teams audio cutting out during meetings.','microsoft teams audio cutting meetings','Multiple users report that their audio cuts out sporadically during Microsoft Teams meetings. Other participants can still hear them, but they cannot hear the others. No known network changes or updates have been applied recently.  This severely impacts communication.','Resolved','USER00047','ServiceDeskAgent3','2024-10-27 16:30:00.000000','Phone','High','High','AudioEngineer1','2024-10-27 18:00:00.000000',NULL,NULL),(1022,'INC001012','Forgotten password reset failing – account locked.','forgotten password reset failing account locked','User’s account is locked after multiple incorrect password attempts. The automated password reset process is failing. They are unable to access any company resources. A manual reset is required to regain access.','New','USER00019','ServiceDeskAgent1','2024-10-27 17:00:00.000000','Phone','Medium','Medium',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(1023,'INC001013','Wi-Fi slow and unstable in conference room A.','wi fi slow unstable conference room','Users in conference room A are experiencing slow and unstable Wi-Fi connectivity.  A speed test shows significantly reduced bandwidth compared to other areas. Resetting the access point did not resolve the problem. A potential interference issue is suspected.','Work In Progress','USER00063','ServiceDeskAgent2','2024-10-27 17:30:00.000000','Email','Medium','Low',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(1024,'INC001014','Blackberry device showing \'No Service\' error.','blackberry device showing service error','User reports that their Blackberry device is displaying a \'No Service\' error. The device is not connecting to the carrier network. They\'ve restarted the device with no effect.  This prevents email access and critical mobile communication.','Resolved','USER00005','ServiceDeskAgent3','2024-10-27 18:00:00.000000','Phone','High','High','MobileEngineer1','2024-10-27 19:30:00.000000',NULL,NULL),(1025,'INC001015','Data loss reported - possible file corruption.','data loss reported possible file corruption','User reports that a critical spreadsheet has been corrupted and data is lost. They are unsure how the corruption occurred. A backup restore is required to recover the data. This affects project timelines significantly.','New','USER00041','ServiceDeskAgent1','2024-10-27 18:30:00.000000','Email','High','Medium',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(1026,'INC001016','HR application unavailable – internal server error.','hr application unavailable internal server error','The HR application is currently unavailable, displaying an internal server error message.  Other applications appear to be functioning normally. This is preventing users from accessing pay stubs and benefits information.','Work In Progress','USER00029','ServiceDeskAgent2','2024-10-27 19:00:00.000000','Chat','Medium','Medium',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(1027,'INC001017','Printer queue stuck – jobs not printing.','printer queue stuck jobs printing','Users are reporting that the printer queue is stuck, and jobs are not printing. The printer shows as online and ready. Clearing the print queue manually does not resolve the issue.  The print server logs suggest a resource exhaustion error.','Resolved','USER00058','ServiceDeskAgent3','2024-10-27 19:30:00.000000','Phone','Medium','Medium','PrintEngineer1','2024-10-27 21:00:00.000000',NULL,NULL),(1028,'INC001018','Unable to launch Zoom meetings - error 10007.','unable launch zoom meetings error 10007','Users are reporting an error 10007 when attempting to launch Zoom meetings.  The error message indicates a network connectivity issue.  They are using both company-issued laptops and personal devices.  A workaround has been provided, but a fix is needed.','New','USER00015','ServiceDeskAgent1','2024-10-27 20:00:00.000000','Email','Medium','Medium',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(1029,'INC001019','Cannot access intranet – authentication problem.','access intranet authentication problem','Users are unable to access the company intranet, receiving an authentication problem error.  The intranet service is reachable from the server room.  A possible configuration change may have introduced the error. This hinders access to company policies.','Work In Progress','USER00031','ServiceDeskAgent2','2024-10-27 20:30:00.000000','Chat','Medium','Low',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(1030,'INC001020','Screen sharing frozen in video conference.','screen sharing frozen video conference','During a video conference, one user’s screen sharing froze, preventing others from seeing their presentation. The user\'s computer became unresponsive for a brief period.  A reboot resolved the problem, but the root cause remains unknown.  This happened on a company-provided laptop.','Closed','USER00009','ServiceDeskAgent3','2024-10-27 21:00:00.000000','Phone','Low','Low','ServiceDeskAgent1','2024-10-27 22:00:00.000000',NULL,NULL),(1031,'INC001021','Unable to access shared drive \\\\fileserver\\data after recent updates.','unable access shared drive fileserver data recent updates','User reports inability to access the \\\\fileserver\\data shared drive. They received an \'Access Denied\' error.  They attempted restarting their machine and reconnecting, but the issue persists.  This impacts several team members. Escalated to network team for investigation.','Work In Progress','USER0012','SUPPORT01','2024-10-27 14:15:00.000000','Phone','Medium','Medium',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(1032,'INC001022','Outlook email sending failing for multiple users in marketing.','outlook email sending failing multiple users marketing','Multiple users in the marketing department are reporting that they are unable to send emails via Outlook.  Incoming email is working fine. The error message displayed is \'Cannot send mail.\' Initial checks show no issues with the mail server. A wider investigation is needed to determine the root cause.','New','USER0005','SUPPORT02','2024-10-27 15:30:00.000000','Email','High','High',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(1033,'INC001023','Slow performance with Salesforce after the upgrade.','slow performance salesforce upgrade','Users are experiencing significant slowdowns when using Salesforce, particularly with reports and dashboards. This started shortly after the recent Salesforce upgrade.  They’ve cleared cache and cookies, but the issue persists. This is impacting sales productivity.','Work In Progress','USER0021','SUPPORT01','2024-10-27 16:45:00.000000','Chat','Medium','Medium',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(1034,'INC001024','VPN connection drops unexpectedly every 15 minutes.','vpn connection drops unexpectedly 15 minutes','A user reports that their VPN connection is dropping unexpectedly every 15 minutes. They are working remotely and need reliable access to internal resources. They have tried restarting their laptop and router, without success. Error logs will be reviewed.','New','USER0018','SUPPORT03','2024-10-27 17:10:00.000000','Phone','Medium','Medium',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(1035,'INC001025','Printer J2340 unresponsive; users cannot print documents.','printer j2340 unresponsive users print documents','Users are unable to print to printer J2340. The printer shows as offline. IT has rebooted the printer.  The print queue is empty.  Confirm if the physical cable is connected and no network errors are present.','Resolved','USER0009','SUPPORT02','2024-10-27 18:20:00.000000','Walk-up','Low','Low','TECH05','2024-10-27 18:45:00.000000',NULL,NULL),(1036,'INC001026','Password reset failed; user locked out of account.','password reset failed user locked account','User attempted a self-service password reset, but the process failed, and they are now locked out of their account. The system indicates an error during the reset process. The user is unable to access any applications. Resetting manually and investigating the password reset service.','Work In Progress','USER0001','SUPPORT01','2024-10-27 19:30:00.000000','Self-Service','Medium','Medium',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(1037,'INC001027','Intermittent audio dropouts on video conference call.','intermittent audio dropouts video conference','User experiencing intermittent audio dropouts during video conference calls using Zoom.  This seems to happen randomly. Other participants report similar issues.  Confirmed user\'s microphone and speakers are working locally.','New','USER0015','SUPPORT03','2024-10-27 20:00:00.000000','Phone','Low','Low',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(1038,'INC001028','Cannot access Teams; receives \'authentication failed\' error.','access teams receives authentication failed error','A user cannot access Microsoft Teams and is receiving an \'authentication failed\' error. They are able to access other Microsoft applications like Outlook.  Tried clearing cache and re-logging in with no effect.  Reviewing authentication logs.','Work In Progress','USER0023','SUPPORT02','2024-10-27 21:15:00.000000','Email','Medium','Medium',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(1039,'INC001029','Website loading very slowly; users are complaining.','website loading slowly users complaining','Users are reporting that the company website is loading very slowly. This is impacting users’ ability to access important information. Network latency is within acceptable ranges.  Checking server resources.','New','USER0007','SUPPORT01','2024-10-27 22:30:00.000000','Phone','High','High',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(1040,'INC001030','Unable to download large files from the shared network drive.','unable download large files shared network drive','Users are unable to download large files from the shared network drive. They are receiving a \'File too large\' error. This is impacting the ability to share data with external partners.  Increasing file size limits in the network share.','Resolved','USER0019','SUPPORT03','2024-10-27 23:45:00.000000','Chat','Medium','Medium','TECH01','2024-10-28 00:30:00.000000',NULL,NULL),(1041,'INC001031','SSO login failing sporadically; impacting application access.','sso login failing sporadically impacting application access','Users are experiencing intermittent failures when logging in through Single Sign-On (SSO). This is impacting access to various applications. The issue appears to be random. This is a critical issue affecting productivity across the organization.','Work In Progress','USER0025','SUPPORT01','2024-10-28 13:00:00.000000','Email','High','High',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(1042,'INC001032','User’s laptop won\'t connect to Wi-Fi; seeing incorrect password prompt.','user s laptop won t connect wi fi seeing incorrect password prompt','A user\'s laptop is unable to connect to the Wi-Fi network. They are seeing a prompt indicating an incorrect password. They are certain they\'re using the correct credentials. Resetting network configuration and validating SSID.','New','USER0003','SUPPORT02','2024-10-28 14:15:00.000000','Phone','Low','Low',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(1043,'INC001033','Adobe Creative Suite licenses exhausted; users cannot install.','adobe creative suite licenses exhausted users install','Users are unable to install Adobe Creative Suite software due to license exhaustion. This is preventing designers from completing their work. Checking license server and adding additional licenses.','Resolved','USER0011','SUPPORT03','2024-10-28 15:30:00.000000','Email','Medium','Medium','TECH02','2024-10-28 16:00:00.000000',NULL,NULL),(1044,'INC001034','Screen sharing frozen during Zoom meeting with external client.','screen sharing frozen zoom meeting external client','During a Zoom meeting with an external client, the user\'s screen sharing froze. The client was unable to see the presentation. Restarting Zoom and checking network connectivity. User reported the client felt unprofessional due to the interruption.','Closed','USER0020','SUPPORT01','2024-10-28 17:00:00.000000','Phone','Low','Low','TECH04','2024-10-28 17:30:00.000000',NULL,NULL),(1045,'INC001035','User reports data loss from corrupted hard drive.','user reports data loss corrupted hard drive','User reports data loss due to a corrupted hard drive. They suspect a recent power surge may have been the cause.  Immediate steps include data recovery and forensic analysis.  User is being provided a temporary replacement device.','Work In Progress','USER0006','SUPPORT03','2024-10-28 18:15:00.000000','Phone','High','High',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(1046,'INC001036','Unable to access Salesforce; error 403 forbidden.','unable access salesforce error 403 forbidden','User reports they can no longer access Salesforce. They receive a 403 Forbidden error when attempting to log in. They\'ve tried clearing their browser cache and cookies, but the issue persists. Impacting sales team productivity.','New','USER00012','Helpdesk','2024-11-12 18:15:00.000000','Phone','High','High',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(1047,'INC001037','Laptop screen flickering; intermittent display issues.','laptop screen flickering intermittent display issues','User reports their laptop screen is flickering intermittently. They state it started this morning and seems to worsen when running multiple applications. A reboot did not resolve the problem. They are using a company-issued Dell Latitude.','Work In Progress','USER00028','Helpdesk','2024-11-12 18:45:00.000000','Email','Medium','Medium',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(1048,'INC001038','Printer queue stuck; jobs not printing.','printer queue stuck jobs printing','The HP LaserJet 4000 printer is experiencing issues with its print queue. Users are reporting jobs are stuck and not printing. The print spooler service has been restarted with no effect.  Requires immediate attention due to departmental deadlines.','Resolved','USER00005','Helpdesk','2024-11-12 19:10:00.000000','Walk-up','Medium','Medium','Technician1','2024-11-12 20:30:00.000000',NULL,NULL),(1049,'INC001039','Slow VPN connection; very sluggish data transfer.','slow vpn connection sluggish data transfer','User reports significantly slow VPN connection speeds, making file transfers extremely slow. They checked their local internet speed, which is normal. The VPN server is experiencing high latency. Affecting remote workers.','Work In Progress','USER00035','Helpdesk','2024-11-12 19:40:00.000000','Email','Medium','Medium',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(1050,'INC001040','Unable to access shared drive – permissions issue?','unable access shared drive permissions issue','User cannot access a shared network drive. They receive an \'Access Denied\' error. They were recently moved to a new team, which may have affected their permissions. The drive contains critical project files.','Resolved','USER00018','Helpdesk','2024-11-12 20:00:00.000000','Phone','High','High','Technician2','2024-11-12 21:15:00.000000',NULL,NULL),(1051,'INC001041','Teams audio cutting out during video calls.','teams audio cutting video calls','Multiple users are experiencing audio dropouts during Microsoft Teams video calls. The issue seems random and affects different devices. This is hindering team collaboration and client meetings.','New','USER00041','Helpdesk','2024-11-12 20:30:00.000000','Chat','Medium','Medium',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(1052,'INC001042','Can\'t login to Jira – SSO failure reported.','t login jira sso failure reported','Users are unable to login to Jira, with error messages pointing to a Single Sign-On (SSO) failure.  Recent changes were made to the SSO configuration. IT security has